author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week on the show, writers Collin Kelly and Jackson Lanzing join the podcast to discuss the new Giant-Size X-Men anniversary event featuring Ms. Marvel. We’re also joined by Marvel Games’ Tom Tao and Netease’s Robin Bao to hear all about the upcoming mobile RPG, Marvel Mystic Mayhem. And if you’re dying to know more about the Silver Surfer, we’ve got a full comic book breakdown just for you! 

00:00 - Welcome Back!
02:31 - Writers Collin Kelly and Jackson Lanzing on the Giant-Size X-men anniversary w/ Ms. Marvel
13:46 - Marvel Games’ Tom Tao and Netease’s Robin Bao talk Marvel Mystic Mayhem
25:38 - Silver Surfer comic book breakdown
